        {
            "title": "乘聯分會：3月首9日全國乘用車新能源市場零售按年升44%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">乘聯分會發表3月份最新數據，顯示本月首9日，全國乘用車新能源市場零售20.4萬輛，按年增長44%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240711_FI_source-ap_China_Auto_Sales.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240711_FI_source-ap_China_Auto_Sales.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若與較上月同期比較，增長更達1.16倍；今年以來累計零售163萬輛，較去年同期升36%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內全國乘用車市場零售36.4萬輛，按年升14%，按月增52%。今年以來累計零售353.9萬輛，年增2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14771240-%e4%b9%98%e8%81%af%e5%88%86%e6%9c%83%ef%bc%9a3%e6%9c%88%e9%a6%969%e6%97%a5%e5%85%a8%e5%9c%8b%e4%b9%98%e7%94%a8%e8%bb%8a%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250303_FI_source-ap_China_New_Cars_Sales-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-12 16:50:33",
